| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1160 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1e6b8a0c-ff71-570d-b4e6-8c6a6eee0629"
